Ledger

You have bills to pay every week! Employees and advertising are not free. You have to balance your prices with your expenses. Click on the "Ledger" button on your control panel to see how much you have been paying in expenses each week.

Don't be a loss leader - A loss leader is someone who sells one product at a loss to make money on a related, more expensive item. In Blackwood, this strategy will not be effective. 